text: Kamran Afzal (born 28 February 1997) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his List A debut on 20 January 2017 for Lahore Whites in the 2016–17 Regional One Day Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Lahore Whites cricketers Category:Cricketers from Lahore
